# Test command with positional parameters in MAP query
# First test with a simple map using positional parameters
query_positional 'MAP { val1: $1, val2: $2 }' 123 456
---
> +--------+--------+
> |  val1  |  val2  |
> +--------+--------+
> |  123   |  456   |
> +--------+--------+
>
